"comment">#或</span></span><br><span class="line">rasa train</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/00831rSTly1gch32z6o3nj319q07ywmb.jpg" alt=""></p><h2 id="PART-V"><a href="#PART-V" class="headerlink" title="PART V"></a>PART V</h2><p><code>endpoints.yml</code></p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/00831rSTly1gch3azucdaj30lo04ggnm.jpg" style="zoom:67%;" /><p><code>action.py</code></p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/00831rSTly1gch5eqhcm3j30sg0ratpi.jpg" style="zoom:50%;" /><h2 id="PART-VI"><a href="#PART-VI" class="headerlink" title="PART VI"></a>PART VI</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 启动Rasa server</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 该服务实现自然语言理解(NLU)和对话管理(Core)功能</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 注：该服务的--port默认为5005，如果使用默认则可以省略</span></span><br><span class="line">python3 -m rasa run --port 5005 --endpoints configs/endpoints.yml --credentials configs/credentials.yml --debug</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 启动action server</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 注：该服务的--port默认为5055，如果使用默认则可以省略</span></span><br><span class="line">Python3 -m rasa run actions --port 5055 --actions actions --debug</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>创建server.py</code></p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/00831rSTly1gch5jfcy8rj30u00x3qpk.jpg" style="zoom:50%;" /><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 启动server.py</span></span><br><span class="line">python3 server.py</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="PART-VII"><a href="#PART-VII" class="headerlink" title="PART VII"></a>PART VII</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python3 -m rasa train --config configs/config.yml --domain configs/domain.yml --data data/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python3 -m rasa run --port 5005 --endpoints configs/endpoints.yml --credentials configs/credentials.yml --debug</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Python3 -m rasa run actions --port 5055 --actions actions --debug</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python3 server.py</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
